OL,3,CBank of England will monitor cash
OL,4,Cacceptance on ongoing basis
OL,6,FThe Government has said the Bank of
OL,7,FEngland will monitor cash acceptance
OL,8,Fon an ongoing basis, following a
OL,9,FTreasury Committee report which raised
OL,10,Fconcerns about the future of coins and
OL,11,Fbanknotes.
OL,13,FIn its response to the report, the
OL,14,FGovernment said the Bank had committed
OL,15,Fto continuing to include an additional
OL,16,Fquestion on cash acceptance in its
OL,17,Fsurvey of consumers, after it was
OL,18,Fintroduced in January.
