OL,6,FThe response said: "The Bank of
OL,7,FEngland regularly collects data on
OL,8,Fconsumers' payment preferences,
OL,9,Fincluding the consumer experience of
OL,10,Fcash acceptance. In January, the Bank
OL,11,Fof England expanded this data
OL,12,Fcollection with a new question seeking
OL,13,Fto understand the impact of a business
OL,14,Frefusing cash on individuals.
OL,16,F"Where consumers did encounter a cash
OL,17,Ffree store, 8% had to go to a
OL,18,Fdifferent store to complete their
OL,19,Fpurchase and 6% did not purchase the
OL,20,Fitem they wanted at all.
