OL,6,F"The Bank of England has committed to
OL,7,Fcontinuing to include this additional
OL,8,Fquestion on cash acceptance in its
OL,9,Fsurveys of consumers, allowing the
OL,10,FGovernment another avenue to monitor
OL,11,Fcash acceptance levels and the impact
OL,12,Fof cash acceptance on an ongoing
OL,13,Fbasis, alongside data from industry."
OL,15,FThe committee has highlighted how UK
OL,16,Fbusinesses and organisations can
OL,17,Fchoose to refuse cash with no legal
OL,18,Fduty to accommodate customers' varying
OL,19,Fneeds.
