OL,3,CBank of England will monitor cash
OL,4,Cacceptance on ongoing basis
OL,6,FIts report, published earlier this
OL,7,Fyear, warned that a lack of action to
OL,8,Ftackle declining cash acceptance could
OL,9,Flead to a two-tier society with the
OL,10,Fmost vulnerable bearing the cost. MPs
OL,11,Fcalled for improved monitoring.
OL,13,FThe committee highlighted that
OL,14,Fvulnerable groups, such as people with
OL,15,Flearning disabilities, domestic abuse
OL,16,Fvictims and the elderly, could be
OL,17,Fparticularly affected.
