OL,6,FBut the committee's report argued that
OL,7,Fthere may come a time in the future
OL,8,Fwhen it becomes necessary for the
OL,9,FTreasury to mandate cash acceptance if
OL,10,Fthose who rely on physical cash are
OL,11,Fnot adequately supported.
