OL,6,FTreasury Committee chairwoman Dame Meg
OL,7,FHillier said: "The commitment from the
OL,8,FBank of England to continue monitoring
OL,9,Fcash acceptance is a positive first
OL,10,Fstep but given the Government agree
OL,11,Fwith our views in the main, we expect
OL,12,Fto see further positive measures on
OL,13,Fprotecting the most vulnerable when
OL,14,Fthey publish their Financial Inclusion
OL,15,FStrategy."
